<emphasis id="09A7614BFA1F3F3EA2CFAB96C605517D" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84">Figure 20.</emphasis>
Distribution of 
<taxonomicName id="427993A74458804E8D9A1097D868CB36" class="Arachnida" genus="H." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="H. isambertoi" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="isambertoi">
<emphasis id="1F9D98B415C39E78917B461084431E14" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84">H. isambertoi</emphasis>
